org.apache.flink.mesos.scheduler

类 SchedulerProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.mesos.scheduler.SchedulerProxy
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.apache.mesos.Scheduler

    public class SchedulerProxy
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.mesos.Scheduler
    This class reacts to callbacks from the Mesos scheduler driver.

    In order to preserve actor concurrency safety, this class simply sends corresponding messages to the Mesos resource master actor.

    See https://mesos.apache.org/api/latest/java/org/apache/mesos/Scheduler.html
